-install osgeo4w and select the following packages:
  gdal-python
  python-numpy
  python-requests
  python-future
  wxpython

-dowload pymodis from https://pypi.python.org/pypi/pyModis
Now decompress and Enter inside the new directory
    cd pyModis

Install the library with root permission
    python setup.py install

Now we can try to load the library so
    python

    Python 2.6.6 (r266:84292, Oct  9 2010, 11:40:09) 
    [GCC 4.4.5] on linux2
    Type "help", "copyright", "credits" or "license" for more information.
    >>> import pymodis
    
install Certificate verification via pip    
  pip install certifi
  pip install urllib3[secure]
  
